<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> See Chapter XXXV of <a href="http://www.marxists.org/archive/trotsky/works/1930-lif/ch35.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.marxists.org/archive/trotsky/works/1930-lif/ch35.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>My Life</i></a></li>
