<li id="cite_note-Testament-44">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Testament_44-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Testament_44-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="http://www.newyouth.com/archives/classics/trotsky/trotsky_testament.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.newyouth.com/archives/classics/trotsky/trotsky_testament.asp" rel="nofollow">"Trotsky's Testament"</a> (February 27, 1940) Retrieved August 27, 2007</li>
