<li id="cite_note-47"><b><a href="#cite_ref-47" title="">^</a></b> Walsh, Lynn, <a href="http://www.marxist.net/trotsky/life/life.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.marxist.net/trotsky/life/life.htm" rel="nofollow">The Assassination of Trotsky</a>, <i>Militant International Review</i>, Summer 1980, retrieved on 2007-07-29.</li>
<li id="cite_note-48"><b><a href="#cite_ref-48" title="">^</a></b> <i>Australian Associated Press,</i> <a href="http://150.theage.com.au/view_bestofarticle.asp?straction=update&amp;inttype=1&amp;intid=1188" class="external text" title="http://150.theage.com.au/view_bestofarticle.asp?straction=update&amp;inttype=1&amp;intid=1188" rel="nofollow">Death of Leon Trotsky</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Age" title="The Age">The Age</a></i> 150th Anniversary edition reprint, 1940-08-23, Retrieved on 2007-03-22.</li>
<li id="cite_note-49"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49" title="">^</a></b> Joseph Choonara, <a href="http://www.isj.org.uk/index.php4?id=397&amp;issue=117" class="external text" title="http://www.isj.org.uk/index.php4?id=397&amp;issue=117" rel="nofollow">"The United Front"</a> in <a href="/wiki/International_Socialism_(journal)" title="International Socialism (journal)">International Socialism</a> 117</li>
